<section id="Viewing_the_SmartProxy_Summary" remap="TID_15085">
	<title>Viewing the SmartProxy Summary</title>
	<para>
		Use the <guilabel>Server Summary</guilabel> to see the member virtual machines.
	</para>
	<procedure>
		<title>To View the SmartProxy Summary</title>
		<step>
			<para>
				Navigate to <menuchoice><guimenu>Configure</guimenu><guisubmenu>Smartproxies</guisubmenu></menuchoice>.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				Click the SmartProxy that you want to view. The summary is automatically displayed.
			</para>
		</step>
		<step>
			<para>
				If you have navigated away from the summary, click <guilabel>Properties</guilabel>, then <guilabel>Summary</guilabel>.
			</para>
		</step>
	</procedure>
</section>